  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How much could have been done, it remains an open question, and-- and certainly is questionable enough not to be very firm about condemning anyone and-- and anybody [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] at least until late '43 or middle of '43 or '44, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when perhaps the Allies could have done a lot more than-- than-- well, I shouldn't say a lot more.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Could have done something, because essentially nothing was done.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] we were all told in our city, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] through placards and through announcements in-- in-- in Hungarian small towns-- there used to be what-- public proclamations.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a-- a uniformed man who would go around and bang on a drum and people would collect and he would read-- read out the latest regulations or rules issued by whatever authorities.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were told that, one fine morning at 4:00, we all have to be ready and packed and we could take, I don't remember, about 50 kilos of belongings and food to-- with us and to be ready to be moved into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Which was a pretty makeshift affair in-- in our town, in part because it was, you know, a relatively godforsaken, primitive area on the one hand.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And on the other hand, because they knew that it was going to be here for a very brief period.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So essentially all that was done is that one [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] area of this-- on either side of this [INAUDIBLE] street, was designated as the ghetto, and families were, when we were driven out of our homes, we went in there and the family settled in with whomever they could.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was kind of rough and tumble.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
